window.bookSummaryJSON = "Mrs. Piggle-Wiggle loves everyone, and everyone loves her right back. The Children love her because she is lots of fun. Their parents love her because she can cure children of absolutely any bad habit. The treatments are unusual, but they work! <p>Who better than a pig, for instance, to teach a piggy little boy table manners? And what better way to cure the rainy-day \"waddle-I-do's\" than hunt for pirate treasure in Mrs. Piggle-Wiggle's upside-down house?</p>"; 
